main event: Observer sighted two spherical objects side by side in the Far East on 18/10/62.
interesting points: The objects were sighted for 2-3 minutes with no sound,They were seen moving without any apparent maintenance of satellite trajectory,The first object was seen at 320 degrees azimuth at 90 degrees altitude,The second object was sighted at 100 degrees azimuth at 60 degrees altitude,Conclusion states insufficient data for evaluation as they may be satellites.
